OL,3,CSTV losses could see the end of the
OL,4,Cold Grampian region
OL,6,GSo the end looms for what was once
OL,7,GGrampian ` the wee station with the
OL,8,Gbig name.
OL,10,FIt lost its name and local programmes
OL,11,F20 years ago but its news service
OL,12,Flived on.
OL,14,FThe STV News at Six in the northern
OL,15,Fhalf of Scotland was really North
OL,16,FTonight in disguise.
OL,18,FNow it too is to go.
OL,20,FSTV is proposing to change its news
OL,21,Fservice.
